<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَمَا الطَّرِيْقَةُ إِلاَّ نَهْجُ أحْمَدَ مَعْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَصْحَابِهِ السَّادَةِ الغُرَّ الصَّنَادِيْدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَأَخْلِصْ لِرَبَّكَ وَاتبْعْ نَهْجَ سَيَّدِنا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قَوْلاً وَفِعْلاً تَنَلْ فَوْزاً بِتَسْدِيْدِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ثَعَالِبُ السُّوْءِ نَادَتْ في أرَانِبِهَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هَذَا زَمَانُكِ عِيْشِيْ عَيْشَ مَحْمُوْدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَا في الأَنَامِ حمُاَةٌ غَيْرَ مَنْ رَحَلُوا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمَنْ بَقِيَ عِنْدَنَا في زِيَّ مَلْحُوْدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَاغُرْبَةَ الدَّيْنِ وَالإيْمَانِ في زَمنٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَهْلُ الهُدى بَيْنَ مَقْهُوْرٍ وَمَظْهُوْدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إنْ دَامَ هَذَا وَلَمْ يَحْصُلْ لَهُ غَيْرٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>لمْ يُبْكَ مَيْتٌ وَلَمْ يُفْرَحْ بِمَوْلُوْدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَفَارِقِ الكُلَّ لا تَلْوِ عَلى أَحَدٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَرضاً بِأَرْضٍ وَخِلاَناً بِمَوْجُوْدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>مَنْ كَانَ نَأْمَلُهُ في كَشْفِ مُعْضِلةٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَبْدَى بِعُذرٍ وَلا أَجْدَي بِمَقْصُوْدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَأَيُّ أَرْضٍ بِهَا الاسْلامُ في شَرَفٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَسُنَّةُ المُصْطَفَى تَزْهُوْ بِتَجْدِيْدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَيْنَ الفِرَارُ وَأَيُّ الدَّارِ نَلْقَى بِهَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وُلاتَهَا كُلَّ مَيْمُوْنٍ وَمَحْمُوْدِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>عُمْرِيْ غَدَا بَيْنَ وَاشٍ ثُمَّ مُبْتَدِعٍ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>يَا رَبِّ يَسَّرْ بِأنصَارٍ لِتَوْحِيْدِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>